s://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1ee3/dfcd/1319_large.png?m=1771929942", "name": "openclaw", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1ee3/dfcd/1319_normal.png?m=1771929942", "title": "OpenClaw", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/openclaw", "topics": 270, "footer": "", "header": "| OpenClaw | 原名 ClawdBot MlotBot |\r\n|---|---|\r\n| 简介 | 支持本地运行与自动任务执行 |\r\n| 官网| https://openclaw.ai/ |\r\n| Moltbook| https://www.moltbook.com |", "title_alternative": "OpenClaw", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1ee3/dfcd/1319_mini.png?m=1771929942", "stars": 277, "founder_id": 69824, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1319, "parent_node_name": null}, "member": {"id": 1, "username": "Livid", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Livid", "website": "sepia.sol.build", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "Remember the bigger green", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4ca/4238/1_mini.png?m=1775264653", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4ca/4238/1_normal.png?m=1775264653", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4ca/4238/1_large.png?m=1775264653", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4ca/4238/1_xlarge.png?m=1775264653", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4ca/4238/1_xxlarge.png?m=1775264653", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4ca/4238/1_xxxlarge.png?m=1775264653", "created": 1272203146, "last_modified": 1775264653, "pro": 1775303769}, "last_reply_by": "fs418082760", "last_touched": 1775286976, "title": "使用本地模型 Gemma4 来驱动 OpenClaw", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1203472", "created": 1775264732, "deleted": 0, "content": "替换下面指令中的 model ID 为你本地 Ollama 里启动的版本。\r\n\r\n```\r\nopenclaw onboard --non-interactive \\\r\n  --auth-choice custom-api-key \\\r\n  --custom-base-url \"http://127.0.0.1:11434/v1\" \\\r\n  --custom-model-id \"gemma4:31b-it-q4_K_M\" \\\r\n  --custom-api-key \"ollama\" \\\r\n  --secret-input-mode plaintext \\\r\n  --custom-compatibility openai \\\r\n  --accept-risk\r\n```", "content_rendered": "<p>替换下面指令中的 model ID 为你本地 Ollama 里启动的版本。</p>\n<pre><code>openclaw onboard --non-interactive \\\n  --auth-choice custom-api-key \\\n  --custom-base-url \"http://127.0.0.1:11434/v1\" \\\n  --custom-model-id \"gemma4:31b-it-q4_K_M\" \\\n  --custom-api-key \"ollama\" \\\n  --secret-input-mode plaintext \\\n  --custom-compatibility openai \\\n  --accept-risk\n</code></pre>\n", "last_modified": 1775264732, "replies": 21, "id": 1203472}]